OL,3,CStar of Educating Greater Manchester
OL,4,Cbanned from teaching
OL,6,FFormer headteacher and Educating
OL,7,FGreater Manchester star Drew Povey and
OL,8,Fhis brother have been banned from
OL,9,Fteaching after a regulator accused the
OL,10,Fpair of "unacceptable professional
OL,11,Fconduct".
OL,13,FMr Povey and his brother Ross, who was
OL,14,Fthe assistant head at Harrop Fold
OL,15,FSchool in Salford, have been barred
OL,16,Ffrom the profession indefinitely for a
OL,17,Fminimum of two years.
