OL,3,CStar of Educating Greater Manchester
OL,4,Cbanned from teaching
OL,6,FIt follows allegations of pupils being
OL,7,Fremoved from the school register in a
OL,8,Fpractice called 'off-rolling', which
OL,9,Fcould potentially imply the school is
OL,10,Fperforming better than it is.
OL,12,FA panel from the Teaching Regulation
OL,13,FAgency (TRA) found the removal of
OL,14,Fthese pupils was likely to have a
OL,15,Fpositive effect on the school's
OL,16,Fperformance data, including GCSE
OL,17,Fresults.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
