OL,3,CStar of Educating Greater Manchester
OL,4,Cbanned from teaching
OL,6,FMr Povey, who was suspended and later
OL,7,Fresigned in 2018, denied all the
OL,8,Fallegations, while his brother made no
OL,9,Fadmissions in relation to the
OL,10,Fallegations.
OL,12,FAfter his resignation, parents at the
OL,13,Fschool - now called The Lowry Academy
OL,14,F- vowed to fight for Drew to be
OL,15,Freinstated.
OL,17,FAt the time, the former head admitted
OL,18,Fto 'administrative errors' involving a
OL,19,Ffew students, but claimed he was the
OL,20,Fvictim of a personal vendetta.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
