OL,3,CStar of Educating Greater Manchester
OL,4,Cbanned from teaching
OL,6,FThe TRA has now found all the
OL,7,Fallegations put to him, including that
OL,8,Fhe failed to ensure accurate records
OL,9,Fwere maintained and, in doing so,
OL,10,Ffailed to protect pupils from the risk
OL,11,Fof potential harm, to be proven. A
OL,12,Fpanel also concluded his actions were
OL,13,Fdeliberate.
OL,15,FHis brother was not found to have
OL,16,Fcaused, permitted or failed to prevent
OL,17,Fthe amendment of pupil attendance data.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
