OL,4,Cbanned from teaching
OL,6,FHowever, the panel found that all of
OL,7,Fthe other allegations made against the
OL,8,Fformer assistant headteacher were
OL,9,Fproven.
OL,11,FIn two separate TRA prohibition order
OL,12,Freports, each relating to Drew and
OL,13,FRoss Povey, both stated the following:
OL,14,F"The panel was satisfied that the
OL,15,Fconduct of (Mr Povey) amounted to
OL,16,Fmisconduct of a serious nature which
OL,17,Ffell significantly short of the
OL,18,Fstandards expected of the profession.
