OL,3,CStar of Educating Greater Manchester
OL,4,Cbanned from teaching
OL,6,F"Accordingly, the panel was satisfied
OL,7,Fthat (Mr Povey) was guilty of
OL,8,Funacceptable professional conduct."
OL,10,FNumerous character references and
OL,11,Ftestimonials, describing Drew as
OL,12,F'kind', a 'breath of fresh air' and an
OL,13,F'exceptional charismatic leader', were
OL,14,Fconsidered by the panel.
