OL,3,CStar of Educating Greater Manchester
OL,4,Cbanned from teaching
OL,6,FHowever, at a joint hearing in
OL,7,FOctober, Drew Povey's legal
OL,8,Frepresentative accepted on the former
OL,9,Fheadteacher's behalf that he was a
OL,10,F'poor school manager' with the panel
OL,11,Ffinding he had very limited knowledge
OL,12,Fof requirements.
OL,14,FAccording to the TRA report, there was
OL,15,F'little evidence that he had taken
OL,16,Fsteps to address this lack of
OL,17,Fknowledge', leading the panel to
OL,18,Fconclude his conduct could be repeated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
