OL,3,CStar of Educating Greater Manchester
OL,4,Cbanned from teaching
OL,6,FThe panel found that Drew and Ross's
OL,7,Factions had brought the profession
OL,8,Finto disrepute.
OL,10,FThey have both been prohibited from
OL,11,Fteaching indefinitely, meaning they
OL,12,Fcannot teach in any school, sixth form
OL,13,Fcollege, youth accommodation or
OL,14,Fchildren's home in England.
OL,16,FThe two brothers may apply for the
OL,17,Fprohibition order to be lifted in 30
OL,18,FOctober 2026.
